#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "3-minute race in permanent darkness with fog bursts. Headlights-only visibility — pure reflexes. Most overtakes wins. The darkness transforms Enduro into a game of memory and reaction — you can hear cars approaching before you see them."
msgstr "3分鐘的比賽 在永久的黑暗中 霧暴。 只有頭燈的能見度——純粹的反射. 多數勝者勝出. 黑暗把恩杜羅變成了記憶和反應的遊戲——你可以在看到汽車之前聽到汽車靠近."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "3-minute timed race — most overtakes wins"
msgstr "3分鐘計時賽——多數勝出"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
