msgstr "——如果一門大炮下水,另一門則單獨面對全波. 令彼衆生."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:56
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— If the puck stops for 5 seconds, a face-off is called"
msgstr "- 如果停了5秒鐘,就叫對決"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
